  <brief_title>Oral Health Awareness and Oral Hygiene in Insulin Dependent Diabetes Mellitus</brief_title>
  <official_title>Effect of Oral Health Educational Program on Awareness and Oral Health Status of Children With Insulin Dependent Diabetes Mellitus: A Randomized Clinical Trial</official_title>
